0012#STR0012#ALL#VQI: Vendor Quality Index                     
0013#STR0013#ALL#VQI = ( 100 - K ) - Critical Factor     
0014#STR0014#ALL#    CF.: Correction Factor,tabled as a function of SQI       
0015#STR0015#ALL#            K..: Qty. obtained as a function of Acceptance Index(AI
0016#STR0016#ALL#            qx.: Quantity delivered as Factor x    
0017#STR0017#ALL#POI = ( 1 - (Sum       Ni * Di / (
0018#STR0018#ALL# * Nt)) ) * 100
0019#STR0019#ALL#      Being Ni: Quantity delivered in delay   (lot to lot )
0020#STR0020#ALL#            Di: Number of days in delay  (lot to lot )
0021#STR0021#ALL#            Nt: Total qtty. delivered in month  
0022#STR0022#ALL#          Note: When calculating POI, if the no. of days in actual delay is greater than the nro. 
0023#STR0023#ALL#                of days defined in parameter MV_QDIAIPO, the latter will be used. 
